-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Primavera 是世界上最环保的节日之一" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Primavera-Sound-festival-credit-Photo-By-Ricardo-Rubio_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周（1 月 11 日）绿色未来 (AGF) 可持续发展奖揭晓了 2023 年最环保的节日。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/coldplay-eco-friendly-tour-music-of-the-spheres-3072573">随着酷玩乐队的环保巡演，音乐再次站在进步思想的最前沿</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据其<a href="http://www.agreenerfuture.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>上的描述，AGF 是一家“非营利公司，致力于帮助世界各地的组织、活动、节日和场馆提高可持续性并减少对环境的影响。”</p><p>发起创立了世界上第一个绿色活动和节日认证。为了获得认证，AGF 向现场活动组织者提供“独立审核和认证”，他们可以首先通过自我评估申请程序申请认证。该组织的目标是帮助活动“提高资源效率、环境影响”并“最终变得更加可持续”。</p><p>被列为最环保的节日包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST Hyde Park</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sziget-festival">Sziget</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera">Primavera Sound</a> ，它们均于 2023 年获得了 A Greener Future (AGF) 的可持续发展认证。</p><p>其他获奖者包括“We Love Green”、Boom、Boomtown Fair、Dockyard、Northside、OyaFestivalen 和 Tremor Festival。您可以<a href="https://www.agreenerfuture.com/who-is-certified">在此处</a>阅读完整的收件人列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3570570" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570570" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570570" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="我们爱绿色" width="2000" height="1271" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/We-Love-Green-festival-Photo-by-ZOULERAH-NORDDINE_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570570" class="wp-caption-text">我们热爱绿色节 – 图片来源：ZOULERAH NORDDINE_AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> AEG Presents 欧洲节日首席执行官吉姆·金 (Jim King) 在谈到他们的认证时表示：“我们致力于在所有 AEG Presents 欧洲节日上实现我们的绿色目标。世界上最好的活动也可能是最可持续的。 BST 海德公园和 All Points East 再次获得绿色节日认证，证明了节日团队为实现这一雄心壮志而付出的辛勤努力”（来自<a href="https://www.iq-mag.net/2024/01/agf-greenest-festivals-2023/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>IQ</em></a> ）。</p><p> AGF 首席执行官克莱尔·奥尼尔 (Claire O&#39;Neill) 补充道：“AGF 可持续活动框架在过去 15 年中变得非常全面。向所有获得此认证的节日和活动致敬，这是一项不小的壮举。</p><p> “我们不仅需要防止进一步的污染、浪费、排放和生物多样性丧失，而且现在还需要适应气候变化导致的我们周围已经发生的变化。这些节日和活动处于领先地位，给许多人带来了希望，展示了我们如何以不同的方式做事，同时享受大量的乐趣。”</p><p>表彰获奖节日的仪式将于 2 月 27 日在伦敦与 ILMC 合作的绿色活动与创新 (GEI16) 会议上举行。</p><p>与此同时，去年，酷玩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-share-details-of-game-changing-environmental-measures-on-music-of-the-spheres-world-tour-3570067">在其“Music Of The Spheres”世界巡演中分享了他们改变游戏规则的环保措施的细节。</a></p><p>早在 2019 年，由<a href="/artists/chris-martin">Chris Martin</a> 、Jonny Buckland、Guy Berryman 和 Will Champion 组成的乐队就宣布，他们正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-say-wont-touring-live-can-make-touring-environmentally-beneficial-2576854">花时间考虑未来的巡演方式，以使其尽可能环保</a>。</p><p>他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-details-of-sustainable-2022-world-stadium-tour-dates-tickets-3070629">承诺到 2022 年，与之前 2016 年至 2017 年的世界巡演相比，排放量减少 50%</a> 。一年后，数据显示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplays-eco-friendly-tour-has-reduced-their-carbon-emissions-by-nearly-half-3451303">乐队在巡演中的碳排放量减少了 47%</a> 。谈到这一成就，酷玩乐队当时表示：“这是一个良好的开端，我们令人难以置信的团队应该为此感到自豪，但显然仍有改进的空间。”</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-share-details-of-game-changing-environmental-measures-on-music-of-the-spheres-world-tour-3570067">在此处阅读乐队在巡演中实施的绿色措施的完整列表</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-greenest-festivals-of-2023-revealed-in-a-greener-futures-sustainability-awards-3570569">“绿色未来”可持续发展奖中透露的 2023 年最环保节日的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 呼吁反芬太尼立法https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-artist-jelly-roll-makes-plea-for-anti-fentanyl-legislation-3570564?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=country-artist-jelly-roll-呼吁反芬太尼立法Elizabeth AubreySun, 14 Jan 2024 21:42:09 +0000 Music NewsNews..Country https://www.nme.com/?p=3570564 <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="果冻卷" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我参加过的葬礼比我愿意分享的还要多”，这位音乐家本周在向国会发表的一次情感恳求中说道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-artist-jelly-roll-makes-plea-for-anti-fentanyl-legislation-3570564">乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 呼吁反芬太尼立法的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="果冻卷" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rapper-Jelly-Roll-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乡村明星 Jelly Roll 本周向美国国会提出反芬太尼立法的动情呼吁。</p><p>这位真名杰森·德福德的音乐家克服了自己的毒瘾，并向国会表示，虽然他“曾经是问题的一部分”，但现在他希望成为“解决方案的一部分”，并敦促美国立法者通过一项抗芬太尼法案。法律。</p><p>官员们表示，芬太尼在美国每天导致近 200 人死亡，是 45 岁以下美国成年人死亡的主要原因（来自<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2024/jan/13/jelly-roll-anti-fentanyl-bill-congress" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报</em>》）。</a></p><p>这种药物最近经常出现在新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coolio-cause-of-death-accidental-fentanyl-overdose-3427107">例如说唱歌手库里奥去年因意外服用芬太尼过量而死亡</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/priscilla-presley">普雷斯利的</a>儿子纳瓦罗内·加里波第<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priscilla-presleys-son-navarone-garibaldi-speaks-out-on-fentanyl-addiction-my-mum-helped-me-i-was-useless-3567324">最近也公开了他“难以忍受”的芬太尼成瘾，他说这几乎要了他的命，并称赞他的母亲帮助他戒毒。</a></p><p>德福德在<a href="https://www.c-span.org/video/?c5101539/music-artist-jelly-roll-appeals-congress-action-fentanyl-crisis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会</a>发表讲话时说：“我参加过的葬礼比我愿意与大家分享的还要多……我可以坐在这里为我所携带的人们的棺材哭泣几天。深深地爱着，深深地爱在我的灵魂里。好人，不仅仅是吸毒者。叔叔、朋友、表兄弟姐妹、普通人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3570566" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570566" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570566" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Country-Musician-Jelly-Roll-Testifies-To-Senate-Hearing-On-Stopping-The-Flow-Of-Fentanyl-Photo-by-Kent-Nishimura_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570566" class="wp-caption-text">乡村音乐家 Jelly Roll 在参议院听证会上就阻止芬太尼的流通作证 — 图片来源：Kent Nishimura/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“我让我的社区崩溃了。我伤害了人。我是一个没有受过教育的人，在厨房里用我一无所知的药物扮演化学家，就像这些毒贩现在所做的那样，他们将市场上的每种药物与芬太尼混合，然后杀死我们所爱的人。</p><p> “……我建议我们站起来，尽快采取更多行动。”</p><p>目前，国会正在考虑是否批准《芬太尼根除和麻醉品威慑芬太尼法案》，该法案也被称为“抵御芬太尼法案”。</p><p>该法案提议实施制裁和反洗钱战略，以阻止阿片类药物的流动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-artist-jelly-roll-makes-plea-for-anti-fentanyl-legislation-3570564">乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 呼吁反芬太尼立法的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
